	<script type="text/javascript">
		
				
		EP.Clients.FOX.portalGAEnable = true;
		EP.Clients.FOX.ddlGAEnable = true;

		if (EP.Clients.FOX.portalGAEnable && EP.Clients.FOX.ddlGAEnable) {
																		
			AUI().use('google-analytics', function(A) { 
				var contentType = '';
				var authors = 'none';
				var deviceType = '';
				var propertiesStr = "KTTV:UA-33119651-1,FTS:UA-60970644-1,LAKANA:UA-28884848-6";
				var mobilePropertiesStr = "";
				var properties = [];
				var mobileProperties = [];
				
				if (propertiesStr) {
					propertiesStrArr = propertiesStr.split(',');
					if (propertiesStrArr) {
						for (var i in propertiesStrArr) {
							var arr = propertiesStrArr[i].split(':');
							properties.push({'name': arr[0], 'propertyId': arr[1]});
						}
					}
				}
				if (mobilePropertiesStr!="") {
					mobilePropertiesStrArr = mobilePropertiesStr.split(',');
					if (mobilePropertiesStrArr) {
						for (var j in mobilePropertiesStrArr) {
							var arr = mobilePropertiesStrArr[j].split(':');
							mobileProperties.push({'name': arr[0], 'propertyId': arr[1]});
						}
					}
				
				}
				var fields = [
					{'name': 'dimension1', 'value': "KTTV"}
				];
		
				contentType = "index";
				if(contentType == "story" || contentType == "feed-story"){
					contentType = "article";
				}
					
				var customFields =[
					{'name': 'dimension2', 'value': contentType},
					{'name': 'dimension3', 'value': authors}
				]; 
				if(EP.Clients.FOX.GA == null || EP.Clients.FOX.GA == undefined){
											var GA = new EP.Components.Analytics.GA(null, properties, fields);
										GA.pageview(customFields);
					EP.Clients.FOX.GA = GA;
				}
			});
		}

				var anvato = EP.Clients.FOX.Anvato = EP.Clients.FOX.Anvato || {};
		anvato.isShowCaption = anvato.isShowCaption || false;
		anvato.mcpId = anvato.mcpId || "epfox";
		anvato.sdkUrl = anvato.sdkUrl || "https://w3.cdn.anvato.net/player/prod/scripts/anvload.js";
		anvato.accesskey = anvato.accesskey || "anvato_epfox_app_web_prod_b3373168e12f423f41504f207000188daf88251b";

	</script>

    adSlot;

    googletag.cmd.push(function() {
     window.GPTAds = window.GPTAds || {};
     googletag.pubads().enableAsyncRendering();
     var windowWidth = document.body.clientWidth,
                                                tabletMaxSize = 1024;
                             /* need refine to get by 5 sizes: X-Large Large Medium Small X-Small  */
           var mapping = googletag.sizeMapping().addSize(
      [1280, 650], eval('[4,4]')).addSize(
      [tabletMaxSize, 300], eval('[]')).addSize(
      [768, 300], eval('[]')).addSize(
      [641, 300], eval('[]')).addSize(
      [0, 0], eval('[]')).build();
      var isValidSize = function( size ){
       return (size !== '[]' && size !== '[0,0]');
      };
            if(windowWidth < 641) {
              if( isValidSize('[]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }else if(windowWidth < 768) {
              if( isValidSize('[]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }else if(windowWidth < tabletMaxSize) {
              if( isValidSize('[]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }else if(windowWidth < 1280) {
              if( isValidSize('[]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }else {
              if( isValidSize('[4,4]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[4,4]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }
          if(adSlot){
      adSlot.addService(googletag.pubads()).setTargeting('pos', 'skin').setCollapseEmptyDiv(true,true);
      adSlot.setTargeting('pgtype', 'index');
      /* set tag for page level */
      
      window.GPTAds[id] = adSlot;
             fox.ads.responsiveRefresh.push(adSlot);
                           fox.ads.disableInitialLoadRefresh.push(adSlot);
              googletag.pubads().disableInitialLoad();
      
                        /*
                           add to infiniteStoryRefresh if within an ininite-story-ad-refresh container
                           or if the ad is configured as mwsticky-bottom
                        */

                            || $('#' + id).hasClass('ad-mwsticky-bottom')) {
                            fox.ads.infiniteStoryRefresh.push(adSlot);

      googletag.enableServices();
      googletag.display(id);

    });

      [1280, 650], eval('[]')).addSize(
      [tabletMaxSize, 300], eval('[]')).addSize(
      [768, 300], eval('[]')).addSize(
      [641, 300], eval('[320,50]')).addSize(
      [0, 0], eval('[320,50]')).build();

       return (size !== '[]' && size !== '[0,0]');
      };

              if( isValidSize('[320,50]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[320,50]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }else if(windowWidth < 768) {
              if( isValidSize('[320,50]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[320,50]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }else if(windowWidth < tabletMaxSize) {
              if( isValidSize('[]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }else if(windowWidth < 1280) {
              if( isValidSize('[]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }else {
              if( isValidSize('[]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }
          if(adSlot){
      adSlot.addService(googletag.pubads()).setTargeting('pos', 'mr3').setCollapseEmptyDiv(true,true);
      adSlot.setTargeting('pgtype', 'index');
      /* set tag for page level */
      
      window.GPTAds[id] = adSlot;
             fox.ads.responsiveRefresh.push(adSlot);
                           fox.ads.disableInitialLoadRefresh.push(adSlot);
              googletag.pubads().disableInitialLoad();

                           add to infiniteStoryRefresh if within an ininite-story-ad-refresh container
                           or if the ad is configured as mwsticky-bottom
                        */

                            || $('#' + id).hasClass('ad-mwsticky-bottom')) {
                            fox.ads.infiniteStoryRefresh.push(adSlot);

                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }else if(windowWidth < 768) {
              if( isValidSize('[]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }else if(windowWidth < tabletMaxSize) {
              if( isValidSize('[]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }else if(windowWidth < 1280) {
              if( isValidSize('[[300,600],[300,250]]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[[300,600],[300,250]]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }else {
              if( isValidSize('[[300,600],[300,250]]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[[300,600],[300,250]]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }
          if(adSlot){
      adSlot.addService(googletag.pubads()).setTargeting('pos', 'mr1').setCollapseEmptyDiv(true,true);
      adSlot.setTargeting('pgtype', 'index');
      /* set tag for page level */
      
      window.GPTAds[id] = adSlot;
             fox.ads.responsiveRefresh.push(adSlot);
                           fox.ads.disableInitialLoadRefresh.push(adSlot);
              googletag.pubads().disableInitialLoad();
      
                        /*
                           add to infiniteStoryRefresh if within an ininite-story-ad-refresh container
                           or if the ad is configured as mwsticky-bottom
                        */
                        if (   $('.infinite-story-ad-refresh #' + id).length > 0
                            || $('#' + id).hasClass('ad-mwsticky-bottom')) {
                            fox.ads.infiniteStoryRefresh.push(adSlot);
                        }

      googletag.pubads().enableSingleRequest();
      googletag.enableServices();
      googletag.display(id);

      
                         }
    });
   };
   renderAd();
  })( jQuery, AUI() );

    <script type='text/javascript'>
  (function($, A){
   var self = fox.ads,
    id = '_56_INSTANCE_0635_MOD-AD-KTTV_MR_TWO_BASE',
    adSlot;

   
   var renderAd = function(){

    googletag.cmd.push(function() {
     window.GPTAds = window.GPTAds || {};
     googletag.pubads().enableAsyncRendering();
     var windowWidth = document.body.clientWidth,
                                                tabletMaxSize = 1024;
                             /* need refine to get by 5 sizes: X-Large Large Medium Small X-Small  */
           var mapping = googletag.sizeMapping().addSize(
      [1280, 650], eval('[[300,600],[300,250]]')).addSize(
      [tabletMaxSize, 300], eval('[[300,600],[300,250]]')).addSize(
      [768, 300], eval('[]')).addSize(
      [641, 300], eval('[]')).addSize(
      [0, 0], eval('[]')).build();
      var isValidSize = function( size ){
       return (size !== '[]' && size !== '[0,0]');
      };
            if(windowWidth < 641) {
              if( isValidSize('[]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }else if(windowWidth < 768) {
              if( isValidSize('[]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }else if(windowWidth < tabletMaxSize) {
              if( isValidSize('[]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }else if(windowWidth < 1280) {
              if( isValidSize('[[300,600],[300,250]]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[[300,600],[300,250]]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }else {
              if( isValidSize('[[300,600],[300,250]]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[[300,600],[300,250]]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }
          if(adSlot){
      adSlot.addService(googletag.pubads()).setTargeting('pos', 'mr2').setCollapseEmptyDiv(true,true);
      adSlot.setTargeting('pgtype', 'index');
      /* set tag for page level */
      
      window.GPTAds[id] = adSlot;
             fox.ads.responsiveRefresh.push(adSlot);
                           fox.ads.disableInitialLoadRefresh.push(adSlot);
              googletag.pubads().disableInitialLoad();
      
                        /*
                           add to infiniteStoryRefresh if within an ininite-story-ad-refresh container
                           or if the ad is configured as mwsticky-bottom
                        */
                        if (   $('.infinite-story-ad-refresh #' + id).length > 0
                            || $('#' + id).hasClass('ad-mwsticky-bottom')) {
                            fox.ads.infiniteStoryRefresh.push(adSlot);
                        }

      googletag.pubads().enableSingleRequest();
      googletag.enableServices();
      googletag.display(id);

      
                         }
    });
   };
   renderAd();
  })( jQuery, AUI() );

              anvatoPlayer = new EP.Clients.FOX.AnvatoPlayer("playerContainer",config,updateStyle,anvatoPlaylist);
   });  

   $("ul.media-list > li.media").bind( "click", function() {
     play(JSON.parse(this.attributes["data-json"].value));
     var liParentDiv = $(this).closest('.media-data').find('.addthis_toolbox');
     liParentDiv.attr('data-href',$(this).attr('data-href'));
     liParentDiv.attr('data-title',$(this).attr('data-title'));
   });
   function updateStyle(){
    var currentSelected = anvatoPlaylist.currentSelected;
    var Lid = "Li_" + currentSelected.id;
    var Li= $('#'+Lid)[0];
    var currentLi = Li.parentElement.getElementsByClassName("now-playing"); 
    if(currentLi && currentLi.length>0){
     currentLi[0].className = "media";
    }
    Li.className += " now-playing";
    
    $("div > h2#VIDEOS_TITLE")[0].innerHTML = unescape(currentSelected.title);
   }
   function play(videoConfig){
    var newConfig = anvatoPlaylist.getNext(videoConfig);
    newConfig.pInstance = "VIDEOS_MODULE_ANVATO_PLAYER";
    anvatoPlayer.updateVideo(newConfig);
    updateStyle();
    //Virtual Pageview Tracking
    var GA  = EP.Clients.FOX.GA;
    if(GA) {
     var pageUrl = videoConfig.videoPageUrl;
     var customFields=new Array()
        customFields = [];
     customFields.push({'name': 'dimension2', 'value': "video"});
        customFields = customFields.concat(videoConfig.customFields);

     GA.virtualPageview(pageUrl, customFields);
       }
   };
  </script>

   var self = fox.ads,

   var renderAd = function(){

    googletag.cmd.push(function() {
     window.GPTAds = window.GPTAds || {};
     googletag.pubads().enableAsyncRendering();
     var windowWidth = document.body.clientWidth,
                                                tabletMaxSize = 1024;
                             /* need refine to get by 5 sizes: X-Large Large Medium Small X-Small  */
           var mapping = googletag.sizeMapping().addSize(
      [1280, 650], eval('[728,90]')).addSize(
      [tabletMaxSize, 300], eval('[728,90]')).addSize(
      [768, 300], eval('[728,90]')).addSize(
      [641, 300], eval('[320,50]')).addSize(
      [0, 0], eval('[320,50]')).build();
      var isValidSize = function( size ){
       return (size !== '[]' && size !== '[0,0]');
      };
            if(windowWidth < 641) {
              if( isValidSize('[320,50]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[320,50]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }else if(windowWidth < 768) {
              if( isValidSize('[320,50]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[320,50]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }else if(windowWidth < tabletMaxSize) {
              if( isValidSize('[728,90]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[728,90]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }else if(windowWidth < 1280) {
              if( isValidSize('[728,90]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[728,90]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }else {
              if( isValidSize('[728,90]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[728,90]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }
          if(adSlot){
      adSlot.addService(googletag.pubads()).setTargeting('pos', 'banner-middle-1').setCollapseEmptyDiv(true,true);
      adSlot.setTargeting('pgtype', 'index');
      /* set tag for page level */
      
      window.GPTAds[id] = adSlot;
             fox.ads.responsiveRefresh.push(adSlot);
                           fox.ads.disableInitialLoadRefresh.push(adSlot);
              googletag.pubads().disableInitialLoad();

			var isClickEventRefreshAd =  true,
		refreshNum = 100;
	var isShowCopyRight = "false";
	
	$(document).ready(function() {
		var mod = $('#MOD_PHOTOS_MOD-PHOTOS-KTTV'),
			placeholder = 'http://static.lakana.com/lakana-fox-global/theme/images/kttv/placeholder-4x3.jpg';
		
		
		var galleryButtonLoadTimer,
			clickNum = 0,
			$wrapper = mod.find(".wrapper-gallery"),
			$clickRefreshBound;
		
		var galleryVirPageviewTracking = function(e){
			var galleryJson = JSON.parse( $('ul.media-list > li.now-viewing')[0].attributes["data-ga"].value );
			var GA  = EP.Clients.FOX.GA;
			if(GA) {
				 GA.virtualPageview("/virtual"+galleryJson.pageUrl, galleryJson.customFields);
			}
		};
			
		var clickAdRefresh = function(e){
			if(isClickEventRefreshAd){
				clickNum++;
				if(clickNum == refreshNum){
					galleryVirPageviewTracking();
					fox.ads.refreshAds(fox.ads.responsiveRefresh, 'click refresh');
					clickNum = 0;
				}
			}
		};
		var bindClickEventRefreshAd = function(){
			if( $wrapper.find('.owl-next').length > 0 ){
				clearTimeout(galleryButtonLoadTimer);
				$clickRefreshBound = $wrapper.find(".owl-prev, .owl-next").bind('click', clickAdRefresh);
			}else{
				galleryButtonLoadTimer = setTimeout(function(){bindClickEventRefreshAd();},1000);
			}
		}
		var resetClickEventRefreshAd = function(){
			if(isClickEventRefreshAd){
				clearTimeout(galleryButtonLoadTimer);
				if( $clickRefreshBound ){
					$clickRefreshBound.unbind('click', clickAdRefresh);
				}
				bindClickEventRefreshAd();
			}
		};
		resetClickEventRefreshAd();
		
		var lis = mod.find('.more-media ul.media-list > li.media');
		lis.click(clickAdRefresh).children('a').click(function(e) {
			e.preventDefault();
			var activeClass= 'now-viewing';
			
			var $li = $(this).parent().addClass(activeClass);
			lis.not($li).removeClass(activeClass);
			var gallery = galleries[ $li.attr('data-gallery-id') ];
			mod.find('.media-data .media-title').text( gallery.title );
			
			var content = '';
			$.each(gallery.images, function(idx, imgObj){
				var photoCaption = "";
				var photoCopyRight = '';
				if(isShowCopyRight == "true"){
					if(imgObj.copyright == "None" || imgObj.copyright.trim() == ""){
					
					}else if(imgObj.copyright == "Custom"){
						photoCopyRight = imgObj.customCopyright;
					}else{
						photoCopyRight = imgObj.copyright;
					}
				}
				if(imgObj.caption.trim() != ""){
					photoCopyRight = (photoCopyRight == '')?("<div>&nbsp;</div>"):("<div> ?"+photoCopyRight+" </div>");
					photoCaption = imgObj.caption.trim();
					if ((photoCaption.indexOf("<p>") < 0)|| (photoCaption.indexOf("</p>") < 0)){
						photoCaption = "<P>" + photoCaption + "</P>";
					}
					photoCaption = "<figcaption class=\"image-caption\">"+photoCopyRight+"<a class=\"hide-caption\">[&nbsp;<i class=\"fa fa-minus\"></i>&nbsp;] Hide Caption</a> <a class=\"show-caption\">[&nbsp;<i class=\"fa fa-plus\"></i>&nbsp;] Show Caption</a> " +photoCaption+ " </figcaption>";
				}
				var pls = (idx > 0) ? ' placeholder-16x9' : '';
				content += "<figure class=\"item photo crop-photo ratio-16x9"+pls+"\" style=\"background-image: url('" +imgObj.img+ "');\"><img src=\""+placeholder+"\" alt=\"" +imgObj.caption+ "\" title=\"" +imgObj.title+ "\"/>" +photoCaption+ "</figure>";
			});
			
			var $carousel = mod.find('.owl-carousel').first();
			$carousel.html(content);
			$(".image-caption a.hide-caption, .image-caption a.show-caption").click(function(){
				$("figure.item.photo .image-caption").toggleClass('close-caption');
				$("a.hide-caption").toggleClass('close-caption');
				$("a.show-caption").toggleClass('close-caption');
				return false;
			});
			var owl = $carousel.data('owlCarousel');
			owl.reinit( owl.userOptions );
			var liParentDivPhoto = $(this).closest('.media-data').find('.addthis_toolbox');
		 	liParentDivPhoto.attr('data-href',$(this).parent().attr('data-href'));
		 	liParentDivPhoto.attr('data-title',$(this).parent().attr('data-title'));
			
			resetClickEventRefreshAd();
		});
	});
})( jQuery, AUI() );
</script>

                                                                                                                                                        <section class='mod-wrapper mod-ad  delay-bg-load'>
        <div id='_56_INSTANCE_0774_MOD-AD-KTTV_BANNER_BOTTOM_BASE' class='mod-content ad-728 ad-320'></div>
    </section>
    <script type='text/javascript'>
  (function($, A){
   var self = fox.ads,
    id = '_56_INSTANCE_0774_MOD-AD-KTTV_BANNER_BOTTOM_BASE',
    adSlot;

              

    var $slot = $('#'+id),
     $slotWrapper = $slot.parent(),
     lazyLoadWaiting = false;

     

                var onLazyLoad = function(){
                                        if( adSlot ){
                               var refreshOnResize = true;
            self.renderLazyAd( adSlot, refreshOnResize );
                    } else {
                        /* slot hasn't been defined yet */
                        lazyLoadWaiting = true;
                    }
                };

                       
                 $slotWrapper.one(self.LAZY_LOAD_TRIGGER_EVENT, onLazyLoad);
                 
                /* using event trigger in case an outside script wants to trigger instead */
                var triggerLazyLoad = function(){
                               
                     $slotWrapper.trigger(self.LAZY_LOAD_TRIGGER_EVENT);
                                     };

   
   var renderAd = function(){

    googletag.cmd.push(function() {
     window.GPTAds = window.GPTAds || {};
     googletag.pubads().enableAsyncRendering();
     var windowWidth = document.body.clientWidth,
                                                tabletMaxSize = 1024;
                             /* need refine to get by 5 sizes: X-Large Large Medium Small X-Small  */
           var mapping = googletag.sizeMapping().addSize(
      [1280, 650], eval('[728,90]')).addSize(
      [tabletMaxSize, 300], eval('[728,90]')).addSize(
      [768, 300], eval('[728,90]')).addSize(
      [641, 300], eval('[320,50]')).addSize(
      [0, 0], eval('[320,50]')).build();
      var isValidSize = function( size ){
       return (size !== '[]' && size !== '[0,0]');
      };
            if(windowWidth < 641) {
              if( isValidSize('[320,50]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[320,50]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }else if(windowWidth < 768) {
              if( isValidSize('[320,50]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[320,50]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }else if(windowWidth < tabletMaxSize) {
              if( isValidSize('[728,90]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[728,90]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }else if(windowWidth < 1280) {
              if( isValidSize('[728,90]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[728,90]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }else {
              if( isValidSize('[728,90]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[728,90]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }
          if(adSlot){
      adSlot.addService(googletag.pubads()).setTargeting('pos', 'banner-bottom').setCollapseEmptyDiv(true,true);
      adSlot.setTargeting('pgtype', 'index');
      /* set tag for page level */
      
      window.GPTAds[id] = adSlot;
                          googletag.pubads().disableInitialLoad();
      
                        /*
                           add to infiniteStoryRefresh if within an ininite-story-ad-refresh container
                           or if the ad is configured as mwsticky-bottom
                        */
                        if (   $('.infinite-story-ad-refresh #' + id).length > 0
                            || $('#' + id).hasClass('ad-mwsticky-bottom')) {
                            fox.ads.infiniteStoryRefresh.push(adSlot);
                        }

      googletag.pubads().enableSingleRequest();
      googletag.enableServices();
      googletag.display(id);

                                                           
                       /* check for lazy-load scroll class */
                       if( $slotWrapper.hasClass('delay-bg-load') ){
                           $slotWrapper.one('ep-imgloadgroup-load', triggerLazyLoad);
                       } else {
                           /* class might have been removed already */
                           triggerLazyLoad();
                       }
                                                             
                         }
    });
   };
   renderAd();
  })( jQuery, AUI() );
    </script>
    
    </div>

                <script type="text/javascript">
  (function($, A){
    window.taboolaFn = window.taboolaFn || [];

    window.scopeCounter = window.scopeCounter || [];

    window.taboolaFn["showTaboola_infinite_stories_container"] = function() {
     /* Add to Google Tag Manager command chain to ensure commands happen in order */
     googletag.cmd.push(function() {
      window.scopeCounter['infinite_stories_container']++;
      if (window.scopeCounter['infinite_stories_container'] === 1) {
               commonDiv = $("#common_infinite_stories_container");
             }
      var cloneCommon = commonDiv.clone();
      var childDivs = cloneCommon.children('div');
      var newChildDivs = [];
            
      $.each(childDivs, function(idx1, childObj) {
       var $childObj = $(childObj);
       if ($childObj.attr('class') == 'grid-items') {
        $childObj.remove();
       } else {
        newChildDivs.push(childObj);
       }
      });
       
      if (newChildDivs.length > 0) {
       var count = 0;
       $.each(newChildDivs, function(index, childObj) {
        var divId = childObj.getAttribute("id");
        if (divId && divId != null && divId != 'null') {
         if(window.scopeCounter['infinite_stories_container'] >= 1){
          childObj.setAttribute("id", divId + "_" + window.scopeCounter['infinite_stories_container']);
                                                                                              if (childObj.firstChild !== null && childObj.firstChild.className === '_56_INSTANCE_1671_MOD-AD-KTTV_TABOOLA_HOME') {
           var adsDiv = window.taboolaAdCode['_56_INSTANCE_1671_MOD-AD-KTTV_TABOOLA_HOME'];
           adsDiv = adsDiv.replace(/_56_INSTANCE_1671_MOD-AD-KTTV_TABOOLA_HOME/g, "_56_INSTANCE_1671_MOD-AD-KTTV_TABOOLA_HOME_" + window.scopeCounter['infinite_stories_container']);
           var posIndex = (window.scopeCounter['infinite_stories_container'] - 1) % 4 + 1;
           adsDiv = adsDiv.replace(/taboola1/g, "taboola" + posIndex);
           childObj.innerHTML = adsDiv;
                                                                                    }
                   }
        } else {
         //window.scopeContainerIds['infinite_stories_container'][count] = "infinite_stories_containerchild" + count + "_" + window.scopeCounter['infinite_stories_container'];
         childObj.setAttribute("id", 'infinite_stories_container_'+count+'_'+scopeCounter['infinite_stories_container']);
         count++;
        }
       });
       cloneCommon.attr("id", "common_infinite_stories_container" + window.scopeCounter['infinite_stories_container']);
       $("#infinite_stories_container").append(cloneCommon.html());
       if(window.scopeCounter['infinite_stories_container'] >= 1){
                 var adContainerId = "_56_INSTANCE_1671_MOD-AD-KTTV_TABOOLA_HOME_" + window.scopeCounter['infinite_stories_container'];
         var adSlot = (window.GPTAds && window.GPTAds[adContainerId]) ? window.GPTAds[adContainerId] : false;
         if (adSlot) {
          fox.ads.refreshAds([adSlot], 'Rendering Taboola Ad Slot');
         } else {
          fox.utils.log('No Taboola ad slot found for container '+ adContainerId);
         }
               }
      }
      /*if( !window.scopeContainerIds['infinite_stories_container'].length ){
       window.scopeContainerIds['infinite_stories_container'][0] = 'infinite_stories_container';
      }*/
     });

     /* Help sticky plugin now, new content has rendered to recalc height */
     $(window).trigger('reset_sticky_elements');
    }
  })( jQuery, AUI() );

                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[320,50]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }

                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[728,90]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);

                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[728,90]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);

                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[728,90]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);

      window.GPTAds[id] = adSlot;
                          googletag.pubads().disableInitialLoad();

                           add to infiniteStoryRefresh if within an ininite-story-ad-refresh container
                           or if the ad is configured as mwsticky-bottom

                            || $('#' + id).hasClass('ad-mwsticky-bottom')) {
                            fox.ads.infiniteStoryRefresh.push(adSlot);

      googletag.pubads().enableSingleRequest();
      googletag.enableServices();
      googletag.display(id);

                                                           
                       /* check for lazy-load scroll class */
                       if( $slotWrapper.hasClass('delay-bg-load') ){
                           $slotWrapper.one('ep-imgloadgroup-load', triggerLazyLoad);
                       } else {
                           /* class might have been removed already */
                           triggerLazyLoad();

    });
   };
   renderAd();
  })( jQuery, AUI() );

    <script type='text/javascript'>
  (function($, A){
   var self = fox.ads,
    id = '_56_INSTANCE_9amjNdyEzgLM_MOD-AD-KTTV_MWSTICKY',
    adSlot;

   
   var renderAd = function(){

    googletag.cmd.push(function() {
     window.GPTAds = window.GPTAds || {};
     googletag.pubads().enableAsyncRendering();
     var windowWidth = document.body.clientWidth,
                                                tabletMaxSize = 1025;
                        /* for Infinite Story sticky 'mwsticky': 'mwsticky' ad must display on tablet-landscape (1024), but not ANY larger sizes; sticky 'banner-bottom' will only display on desktop (1025+) -- so we need to bump this up to 1025 for these ad positions */
              /* need refine to get by 5 sizes: X-Large Large Medium Small X-Small  */
           var mapping = googletag.sizeMapping().addSize(
      [1280, 650], eval('[]')).addSize(
      [tabletMaxSize, 300], eval('[]')).addSize(
      [768, 300], eval('[728,90]')).addSize(
      [641, 300], eval('[320,50]')).addSize(
      [0, 0], eval('[320,50]')).build();
      var isValidSize = function( size ){
       return (size !== '[]' && size !== '[0,0]');
      };
            if(windowWidth < 641) {
              if( isValidSize('[320,50]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[320,50]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }else if(windowWidth < 768) {
              if( isValidSize('[320,50]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[320,50]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }else if(windowWidth < tabletMaxSize) {
              if( isValidSize('[728,90]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[728,90]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }else if(windowWidth < 1280) {
              if( isValidSize('[]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }else {
              if( isValidSize('[]') ){
                 adSlot = googletag.defineSlot('/63790564/kttv/home', eval('[]'), id).defineSizeMapping(mapping);
               }
            }
          if(adSlot){
      adSlot.addService(googletag.pubads()).setTargeting('pos', 'mwsticky').setCollapseEmptyDiv(true,true);
      adSlot.setTargeting('pgtype', 'index');
      /* set tag for page level */
      
      window.GPTAds[id] = adSlot;
             fox.ads.responsiveRefresh.push(adSlot);
                           fox.ads.disableInitialLoadRefresh.push(adSlot);
              googletag.pubads().disableInitialLoad();
      
                        /*
                           add to infiniteStoryRefresh if within an ininite-story-ad-refresh container
                           or if the ad is configured as mwsticky-bottom
                        */
                        if (   $('.infinite-story-ad-refresh #' + id).length > 0
                            || $('#' + id).hasClass('ad-mwsticky-bottom')) {
                            fox.ads.infiniteStoryRefresh.push(adSlot);
                        }

      googletag.pubads().enableSingleRequest();
      googletag.enableServices();
      googletag.display(id);

      
                         }
    });
   };
   renderAd();
  })( jQuery, AUI() );

	<script>
		function checkSystemDownloadAlertForNewsApp (){
		var useragent = navigator.userAgent.toLocaleLowerCase();
		var index;
		index = useragent.indexOf("android");
		if (index > -1){
			return "android";
		} else {
			index = useragent.indexOf("iphone");
			if(index > -1){
				return "ios"; 
			} else {
				return "";
			}
		}
	}
	
	$(document).ready(function () {
		$.smartbanner({
			title: '#',
			daysHidden: '90',
			daysReminder: '180',
			icon: '#',
			force: checkSystemDownloadAlertForNewsApp(),
			});
	});
	</script>

 <script type="text/javascript">
   var addthis_config = {
           ui_508_compliant: false,
           services_exclude:'10 tag,pinterest_share,print,google,tumblr,aolmail,yahoomail,email',
           services_compact:'facebook,twitter,google_plusone_share,more',
           services_expanded: 'facebook,twitter,google_plusone_share'
    };
	(function($){
		$(document).ready(function() {
			$('.addthis_toolbox').live('mouseover',function(){
				addthis_share.url = $(this).attr('data-href');
				addthis_share.title = $(this).attr('data-title');
				$(this).attr("addthis:url", $(this).attr('data-href'));
				$(this).attr("addthis:title", $(this).attr('data-title'));
				if(addthis){
					addthis.toolbox('.addthis_toolbox',addthis_config, addthis_share);
				}
			})
		});
	})( jQuery);


 </script>
